<th style="background:#ccccff; font-size: 95%; border-top: 1px solid #aaaaaa; border-bottom: 1px solid #aaaaaa; padding: 0 5px 0 5px;"><b>Judaism &amp; other religions</b></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="font-size: 90%; padding: 0 5px 0 5px; background: #ffffff;"><a href="/wiki/Christianity_and_Judaism" title="Christianity and Judaism">Christianity</a> · <a href="/wiki/Judaism_and_Islam" title="Judaism and Islam" class="mw-redirect">Islam</a> · "<a href="/wiki/Judeo-Christian" title="Judeo-Christian">Judeo-Christian</a>" · <a href="/wiki/Alternative_Judaism" title="Alternative Judaism">Others</a></td>
